The paper proposes a method for generating music playlist descriptions using audio content analysis and natural language processing. This involves techniques from several sub-fields of computer science, including speech and audio processing (cs.SD), natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
